FBIS3-54846 "drsov002_e_94001" FBIS-SOV-94-002 Document Type:Daily Report 4 Jan 1994 UKRAINE International Affairs Kiev `Ready' To Swap Warheads for Nuclear Fuel LD0201132094 Moscow Ostankino Television First Channel Network in Russian 1200 GMT 2 Jan 94 LD0201132094 Moscow Ostankino Television First Channel Network Language: Russian Article Type:BFN [Text] The government of Ukraine is ready to start handing over nuclear warheads to Russia as soon as Moscow is able to supply fuel for nuclear power stations as a compensation. This was stated by Aleksandr Shmarov, a vice-premier [as heard] of Ukraine.
